CreateManualAcknowledgement is an ActionForm
    action is AcknowledgeManually
        on completion navigate to ViewAcknowledgementLines
    title is "<DerivedCreateManualAcknowledgement>"
    Layout
        display as text
            single column
                Company.RepresentativeText
                    label is "Company"
                PurchaseOrder
                Buyer.RepresentativeText
                Vendor.RepresentativeText
            two column
                column1
                    PurchaseFromLocation
                    PurchaseOrderDate
                column2
                    ShipToLocation
                    DefaultDeliveryDate
        single column
            PrmAcknowledgementType
            PrmAcknowledgementDate
            PrmAcknowledgementPOShipDate
            PrmAcknowledgementMessage
                use text area of 4 lines
                display as required when (true)
